high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the wall then turn left to face the microwave.
Take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the oven on the other side of the room, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and rinse it off, then pick it up.
Walk to the black stand next to the left of the sink.
Put the potato behind the loaf of bread on the black stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato on the black stand next to the sink.

high_descs: Go to the microwave next to the trash can.
Take the potato out of the microwave.
Go across the room to the sink.
Wash the potato in the sink.
Go to the crate at the end of the counter to the left.
Set the potato down on the crate behind the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato on the crate.

high_descs: Move to stand directly in front of the microwave on the table in the corner.
Remove the brown object from inside the microwave on the table.
Cross the room with the brown object to stand in front of the sink.
Wash the brown object in the kitchen sink and then remove it.
Move to stand in front of the black shelving unit directly to the left of the kitchen counter and sink.
Place the brown object on the top shelf of the shelving unit just behind the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a brown object on a shelving unit from the microwave.
